==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Basque]] ''[[Jainko]]'', [[God]], used in a propaganda song.

===Pronunciation===
IPA: /ˈdʒɪŋgɘʊɪz(ɘ)m/

===Noun===
'''jingoism'''

#(''uncountable'') Excessive [[patriotism]] or [[aggressive]] [[nationalism]]

